nodes.text: The Royal Naboo Security Forces headquarters was located in the capital city of Theed on Naboo. When the Trade Federation invaded the planet in 32 BBY, Captain Kael was pinned down near the building by destroyer droids, but was rescued by Lieutenant Gavyn Sykes.

This building was referred to as RSF headquarters in the 2000 video game Star Wars: Episode I: Battle for Naboo. Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Episode I indicates that the Theed Hangar is the headquarters of the Security Force; this article assumes they are two separate buildings.
